        {
            "title": "JISOO@BLACKPINK亞博館見面會 男粉絲網購門票遇騙 場外報警求助",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"JISOO@BLACKPINK亞博館見面會 男粉絲網購門票疑遇騙 場外報警求助\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2b6eaf27c7c456d671c149dd94a71178/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250329/_2025032921522241558.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">JISOO@BLACKPINK亞博館見面會 男粉絲網購門票疑遇騙 場外報警求助</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO，昨今兩日（3月28至29日）在亞博館舉辦見面會，門票熱賣，但有粉絲疑遇騙，見門入不得。今日晚上8時許，一名43歲男子於亞博館報案，表示自己在網上購買見面會門票，然而最後無法取貨，懷疑受騙遂報案求助。警方其後到場調查，事件中男事主損失約1300元，案件由機場警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方過去曾呼籲市民，應透過官方銷售渠道購票；網購付款前，謹記先查看賣家背景、負評等，或使用 「<a href=\"https://cyberdefender.hk/scameter/\">防騙視伏器</a>」或「防騙視伏App」，輸入可疑平台帳戶名稱、收款帳戶、電話號碼等以評估詐騙風險。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關報道：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/3441278\">JISOO@BLACKPINK空降亞博3.28-29探港粉 台北見面會fans激動推擁大混亂</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4166070/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"JISOO昨今兩日（3月28至29日）在亞博館舉辦見面會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/447aa983b48f31791fea88266cf4848d/2025-03/AWE_1200x690_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        JISOO昨今兩日（3月28至29日）在亞博館舉辦見面會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4166071/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"亞博館。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e677993ba005eec41cdd0dd2242a9c7a/2025-03/DNSG0314ASIAEXPO001.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        亞博館。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4166072/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"亞博館。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d7e7a4510b64b8865f2c40f21c341301/2025-03/DNSG0820AWECOVID008.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        亞博館。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4166075/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO。Instagram\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c3b5962eac30b8c3f9a632661233d99/2025-03/486830277_18295181650266096_7889326076810967294_n.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO。Instagram\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4166074/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO。Instagram\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fde0d1ec43ac191bb59243b80db4455d/2025-03/Snapins_ai_482516272_18292972180266096_5279875042964994105_n_1080.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO。Instagram\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4166073/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO。Instagram\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7651bf7273b9acba5e9d8186ee90a091/2025-03/Snapins_ai_482804044_18510605791049800_2368389184933984418_n_1080.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        韓國人氣女星、女團BLACKPINK成員JISOO。Instagram\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
